These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, epic, scientific, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, funk, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, american, pakistani, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, van, skateboard, motorbike
1. the american is the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the pakistani is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the american is the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1
9. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | thriller   | sports  | scientific  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | hip-hop    | d&b      | funk    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | american | pakistani | japanese |
| Transport     | motorbike  | train       | van    | skateboard     |

