.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, camping, board-games, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, epic, superhero
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, rat, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, surfing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the fish is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the rat and the person who's sport is cricket##2
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person watching superhero movies and the owner of the fish##2
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
9. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading | camping    | board-games  | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror      | mystery  | superhero  | epic |
| Pet           | fish      | rat       | goat      | goldfish       |
| Sport         | baseball    | snowboarding | surfing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, potato, papaya, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, skydiving, dancing
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, coach, designer, police-officer
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, quad-bike, taxi
1. the designer is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the police-officer##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the coach is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person eating papaya and the coach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | potato | papaya     | pumpkin   | pear     |
| Hobby       | woodworking   | card-games   | skydiving | dancing |
| Job         | electrician   | designer | police-officer       | coach    |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | tram | car  | taxi    |

