.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, videographer, designer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, spy, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, turtle, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, climbing, tennis, lacrosse
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is the dancer##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is the videographer##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the doctor is between the owner of the fish and the designer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | dancer  | designer | doctor     | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | comedy  | spy | drama       |
| Pet           | mouse       | ferret    | turtle      | fish           |
| Sport         | cycling | climbing   | lacrosse   | tennis         |

