 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the photographer is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the engineer is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is between the person who's sport is handball and the person watching disaster movies##2
10. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
