4. the journalist is on the left of the thai##1
5. the colombian is the colombian##1
6. the thai is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the thai is on the left of the videographer##1
8. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
9. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
