.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, adventure, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, ambient, d&b, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, polish, egyptian, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, scooter, ship, car
 1. the person driving the car is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is the egyptian##1
 3. the fan of ambient is between the egyptian and the person driving the ship##2
 4. the fan of d&b is the person driving the car##1
 5. the mexican is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the indonesian is the person driving the bus##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the egyptian is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | musical | scientific  | action  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | d&b   | ambient | folk    |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | egyptian   | mexican | polish |
| Transport     | bus    | car   | scooter    | ship  |

