.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, 7up, fanta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, epic, comedy, disaster
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, dog, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, airplane, tram
1. the person watching epic movies is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the motorbike##2
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person driving the train is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching action movies##2
6. the person drinking 7up is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | 7up  | fanta   | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | epic   | action | comedy |
| Pet           | mouse       | dog   | ferret        | hedgehog  |
| Transport     | airplane | train | motorbike         | tram |

