.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, carrot, lime, garlic
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, electrician, dressmaker, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, electronic, pop, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, sailing, water-polo, skateboarding
 1. the person eating carrot is the dressmaker##1
 2. the person eating garlic is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 3. the dressmaker is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 4. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the fan of ambient is the person eating zucchini##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
 7. the electrician is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
 9. the teacher is between the security-guard and the person who's sport is tennis##2
10. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | garlic        | lime    | zucchini | carrot   |
| Job           | security-guard | teacher | electrician   | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | trance       | ambient      | electronic     |
| Sport         | water-polo       | skateboarding | tennis    | sailing  |

