.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, soy-milk, 7up
There 4 different types of food: orange, kale, mango, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, sudoku, singing, gardening
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, mouse, guinea-pig
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person eating orange is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person eating orange and the person eating mango##2
 9. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person eating orange and the person eating mango##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta    | soy-milk    | 7up      | water |
| Food       | orange        | lettuce       | mango       | kale     |
| Hobby      | singing | rock-climbing | gardening | sudoku        |
| Pet        | hedgehog       | guinea-pig     | mouse         | goldfish           |

