 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the fish##2
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the fish is the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | asparagus  | cranberry | grapefruit     | papaya     |
| Pet         | fish | snake | lizard     | rat |
| Sport       | soccer  | volleyball   | climbing | cricket    |
| Transport   | helicopter   | ship   | roller  | quad-bike        |

