.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, water, 7up
There 4 different types of food: onion, strawberry, avocado, eggplant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, zombie, action
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, turkish, chinese
 1. the person drinking coffee is between the chinese and the person drinking water##2
 2. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the turkish is between the person eating avocado and the person eating onion##2
 4. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the chinese##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the turkish##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | 7up         | coffee   | water |
| Food          | strawberry | onion    | eggplant   | avocado   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | zombie | action   | horror   |
| Nationality   | australian | chinese     | turkish | pakistani |

 